---
import DefaultLayout from '../../layouts/DefaultLayout.astro';
const pageTitle = 'Document Scanning Services in India | Tyrus Technologies';
---

<DefaultLayout
  title={pageTitle}
  description="Document scanning services across India. We scan loose sheets, files and bound volumes at high speed with quality checks and secure handling for sensitive records."
>
  <section class="bg-white border-b border-slate-200">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-12">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-emerald-700">
        Services · Scanning
      </p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
        Document scanning services across India.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-3xl text-sm text-slate-700">
        We scan loose sheets, files and bound volumes at high speed, with strong quality checks and
        secure handling for sensitive records. Tyrus Technologies supports hospitals, banks,
        government departments, legal firms and enterprises across India.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-12 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-[1.2fr,1fr]">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">What we scan</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-800">
          <li>• Medical records, case sheets and investigation reports.</li>
          <li>• KYC forms, account opening files and loan documents.</li>
          <li>• Legal case files, contracts and evidence bundles.</li>
          <li>• HR files, employee folders and policy documents.</li>
          <li>• Government archives, land and citizen records.</li>
          <li>• Invoices, purchase orders and finance records.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4 rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 ring-1 ring-slate-200">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Why teams choose our scanning service</h3>
        <ul class="mt-2 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-800">
          <li>• High‑volume scanners with clear image quality.</li>
          <li>• File‑level and box‑level tracking for each batch.</li>
          <li>• Multi‑level image and index quality checks.</li>
          <li>• Secure logistics and controlled access zones.</li>
          <li>• Output formats ready for DMS, EMR or ERP systems.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white border-b border-slate-200">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-12 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Simple, predictable process.</h2>
        <ol class="list-decimal space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-800">
          <li>We receive or pick up documents with secure packing and tracking.</li>
          <li>We prepare files for scanning (removing clips, repairing torn sheets).</li>
          <li>We scan using high‑speed machines suited to your paper size and quality.</li>
          <li>We run image checks and re‑scan any poor‑quality pages.</li>
          <li>We index and name files as per your department’s structure.</li>
          <li>We deliver scanned images and index data in the agreed format.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-3 rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 p-6 ring-1 ring-slate-200">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Outcomes you can expect</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-800">
          <li>• Faster retrieval of case files and records.</li>
          <li>• Free record rooms and storage shelves.</li>
          <li>• Easier audits and compliance checks.</li>
          <li>• Less time spent searching for missing files.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-slate-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-16">
      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500/10 via-sky-500/10 to-slate-100 p-8 ring-1 ring-emerald-200">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
          Plan your document scanning project with us.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
          Share your approximate page volume, file types and location. We will suggest a practical
          scanning model and send you a clear cost estimate.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a
            href="/#cost-calculator"
            class="rounded-full bg-emerald-600 px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-md shadow-emerald-500/40 hover:bg-emerald-700"
          >
            Get a free estimate
          </a>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="rounded-full border border-emerald-300 px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-50"
          >
            Talk to a specialist
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="bg-slate-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-12">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Explore more services</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">Compare related solutions to build the right digitization workflow for your organization.</p>
        <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-sm">
          <a href="/services" class="rounded-full border border-emerald-300 px-4 py-1.5 font-medium text-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-50">All services</a>
          <a href="/industries" class="rounded-full border border-slate-300 px-4 py-1.5 font-medium text-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-100">Industries</a>
          <a href="/blog" class="rounded-full border border-slate-300 px-4 py-1.5 font-medium text-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-100">Read guides</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</DefaultLayout>


